        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin, neutral narrator"
        },
        "text": "宗門廣場上，任務榜高懸。數十名弟子摩拳擦掌，法器丹藥準備齊全。"
