        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin, casual gamer tone"
        },
        "text": "清剿妖獸……難度普通……獎勵靈石一百……"
      },
      {
        "character": "linyi",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin, casual gamer tone"
        },
        "text": "等等，這個「跳過」按鈕是什麼？"
      },
      {
        "character": "linyi",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin, casual gamer tone"
        },
        "text": "「跳過過場動畫，直接領取獎勵」？還有這種好事？點一下試試。"
